@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### 0) Sanidade: API no ar
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Accept: application/json

### 1) Export CSV (chart) - SUCESSO (200 + arquivo CSV)
POST {{baseUrl}}/exports
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/csv

{
  "format": "csv",
  "source_type": "chart",
  "mode": "sync",
  "file_name": "chart_kpi",
  "delimiter": ",",
  "payload": {
    "categories": ["2026-02-01", "2026-02-02", "2026-02-03"],
    "series": [
      { "name": "views", "values": [120, 180, 250] },
      { "name": "conversion_rate", "values": [1.2, 1.4, 1.6] }
    ]
  }
}

### 2) Export CSV (chart) com delimitador ";" - SUCESSO
POST {{baseUrl}}/exports
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/csv

{
  "format": "csv",
  "source_type": "chart",
  "mode": "sync",
  "file_name": "chart_kpi_semicolon",
  "delimiter": ";",
  "payload": {
    "categories": ["Jan", "Feb"],
    "series": [
      { "name": "revenue", "values": [1000, 1500] }
    ]
  }
}

### 3) Export CSV (table) - AINDA NAO IMPLEMENTADO (esperado 501)
POST {{baseUrl}}/exports
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "format": "csv",
  "source_type": "table",
  "mode": "sync",
  "payload": {
    "columns": ["name", "email"],
    "rows": [
      ["Alice", "alice@example.com"],
      ["Bob", "bob@example.com"]
    ]
  }
}

### 4) Export async - AINDA NAO IMPLEMENTADO (esperado 501)
POST {{baseUrl}}/exports
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "format": "csv",
  "source_type": "chart",
  "mode": "async",
  "payload": {
    "categories": ["2026-02-01"],
    "series": [
      { "name": "views", "values": [100] }
    ]
  }
}

### 5) Payload invalido (series com tamanho diferente de categories) - esperado 500 no estado atual
### Obs: quando mapearmos erro de dominio para 400 no handler, esse caso deve virar 400.
POST {{baseUrl}}/exports
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "format": "csv",
  "source_type": "chart",
  "mode": "sync",
  "payload": {
    "categories": ["2026-02-01", "2026-02-02"],
    "series": [
      { "name": "views", "values": [100] }
    ]
  }
}

### 6) Requisicao invalida (sem payload) - esperado 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/exports
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "format": "csv",
  "source_type": "chart",
  "mode": "sync"
}
